quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  88,19,"Ni matumbi yagatite kasimichidwe?"
  88,20,"Ni litaka yalyatite katandichidwe?"
  88,21,"Basi kumbusyani, chisimu mmwejo ni nkukumbusya."
  89,16,"Nambo ndema jaakun'dinga pakunnandiyichisya lisiki lyakwe, akasatiji: “Ambuje ŵangu anjalwisye.”"
  89,17,"Ngwamba! Nambo kuti ngankwatendelaga yaukoto ŵanache ŵawina."
  89,18,"Soni ngankuchisyanaga yaagaliisya masikini."
  90,10,"Ni tun’jongolele matala gaŵili (lyambone ni lyakusakala, kuti jusagule lyajukusaka)."
  90,11,"Ana pakwete pajujesile litala lyamwitumbi (lyalikam’bikasye ku Mbepo)?"
  90,12,"Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya litala lyamwitumbi?"
  91,7,"Kwisa soni ntima ni Juŵaukolosisye."
  91,8,"Basi ni jwaumanyisye yakusakala yakwe ni yambone yakwe."
  91,9,"Pamasile paapundile jwauswejesye (ntima wakwe)."
  92,4,"Chisimu itendo yenu iŵele yakulekangana-lekangana."
  92,5,"Sano mundu jwaakutola (petala lya Allah) ni kuŵa niwoga (wakun'jogopa Jwalakwe)."
  92,6,"Ni kulupilila yambone nnope (yatakalipidwe ligongo lyakutola)."
  93,1,"Nguulumbila nsana."
  93,2,"Ni chilo ndema jachikutulala."
  93,3,"Ngananneka Ambuje ŵenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) soni nganam'benga."